Class PlayerObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.objects.GameObject
      • server.objects.PlayerObject

  • public class PlayerObject
extends GameObject
    Player object. Create for each player, Player also is game object. This class provides common player movements and operation such a keys/gates operation.
    Author:
    Mark Birger (xbirge00), Daniil Khudiakov (xkhudi00)
